textAnnotations.description:
A HOME LOAN OFFER
SO GOOD YOU DON'T
NEED A CELEBRITY
ANZ
= AN
A home loan offer so
good...
Take out an eligible home loan over
$300k and you could get the home, the
points, plus the chance to win up to
half a million dollars' off your loan. Who
needs a celebrity?
Apply by 31 August 2019 and settle by 31 January
2020. See full terms and conditions (PDF 454kb).
